        <h2 class="-f-topLine-center">How Hughes Home Services Ottawa Got Started</h2>
        <div class="spread -sp-2Col_split-1">
            <p>Hughes Home Services Ottawa was inspired by the early days of helping out with my father’s small general contracting
                company. As a teenager, I joined him in assisting homeowners with tasks around the house, and I saw firsthand how
                grateful people were for our help. These experiences sparked my dream of running my own business.</p>
            <p>Over 30 years ago, I started a home fitness and personal training business, while still doing handyman jobs on the
                side during evenings and weekends. A few years before COVID, I decided to take my handyman services full-time, not
                knowing the demand for home services would increase so quickly. Since then, I’ve hired a dedicated team, acquired a
                truck, and continued to grow Hughes Home Services into the company it is today.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>


